    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Instalando y configurando Octopress]]></title>
    <link href="http://mirabalj.github.io/blog/2013/08/19/instalando-y-configurando-octopress/"/>
    <updated>2013-08-19T11:07:00-04:30</updated>
